item.title: A very spoiled brown husky that has traveled to all 48 states!
item.author: youremail@domain.com (Some Person)
item.description: 2020-11-26 09:46:40 Source: MiB Photography Community Report This distinctive husky made its debut on the social world section of the social media site Instagram. Unlike other huskies, this dog has a husky body and sapphire blue eyes, but his hair is brown. It’s very new, and it looks like a gray tree trunk. “The Quoi Husky is actually not exactly brown in appearance. It still has a small white spot on its chest, and how many huskies do you see that look like it?
